{"tid":1734703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地 唔好信社署社工 講到天花龍鳯都唔好信","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T15:39:19.000Z","uid":172713,"like":159,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":110,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d90848a8774736734cda49722f03c2db48355c","tid":1734703,"uid":172713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已fc<br />\n100個SWO(社工)&amp;CP (臨床心理學家)from correction and youth branch已經係胡忠出旅遊巴出發<br />\n</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好問我點解會知，你懂的！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">佢哋係黎勸你地自首，仲會講到好好聽，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好信</span></span>！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">16歲以下要有成人陪同先可錄口供，擺到明有心靠害，入曬你地罪，仲要呢班高層好多都係老屎忽藍絲<br />\n<br />\n求下你地，再緊持多陣，我地成班手足努力緊，好多人已經打左1日1夜，更多人支援黎緊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚就算被狗打到跪係地下，都要救曬你地岀黎！ ！</span>[/b]</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n驅除共黨，還我香港<br />\n寧化飛灰，不作浮塵</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c89fa620ad1aebc71646c7a3c9828206d87e4ef5","tid":1734703,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:37:55.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ixwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=91714b6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: gold;\"> /task3</span> <br />\n<br />\n最新Task分類<br />\n/task1: 法案、抗爭活動<br />\n/task2: BNO、中國、其他香港議題<br />\n/task3: !!!! #PolyU !!!!<br />\n/task4: 日韓德任務"},{"pid":"361d0dc536d1c3f77503803bf40b7810f5d0ee4e